text.tspan: This template can be used to make
graphics and overlays for video production.
The components here can be copy-pasted into
the "page" to provide a common look/theme
across all the video.
Any space that is left blank will be transparent
in the video. If there is a video layer behind it,
you will still be able to see it.
Once you have the screen how you like it, click
the Export button. Then in the menu select the
"Page" button. Pick a file name that ends in
".png" (this will preserve the transparency and
give good quality), then click the export button.
This file can now be imported into the broadcast
software.
